channel.title: 614 Akward Run Error
channel.description:
So i recently got a 614 fullscreen client, got done downloading cache, and i downloaded a source. And now i just got done with that.. I was thinking to myself. Holyshit, this is kind of cool. So i run the server, and it gives me this error lmfao.. [code][20:42:44] [Server] Starting loading Cache... java.lang.NullPointerException at RuneExtream.rscache.CacheManager.load(CacheManager.java:18) at RuneExtream.rscache.Cache.<init>(Cache.java:17) at RuneExtream.Server.<init>(Server.java:28) at RuneExtream.Server.main(Server.java:68) Press any key to continue . . . [/code] Anybody wanna fix me?
PS: I have teamviewer.
